{"tid":2144171,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[專職醫療][核酸檢測支援隊]《醫務化驗師（特別豁免）規例》明日生效","createTime":"2020-08-07T14:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T14:36:31.000Z","uid":81046,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"baaa4187df1d5e946b2cc840283e323fb6abb5c6","tid":2144171,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202465e/cs220202465153.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20202465e%2Fcs220202465153.pdf&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6B6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=79c61b56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202465e/cs220202465153.pdf</a><br />\n本規例自 2020 年 8 月 8 日起實施。<br />\n<br />\n政府於今日刊憲訂立《醫務化驗師（特別豁免）規例》，臨時豁免核酸檢測支援隊在《輔助醫療業條例》（第359章）下在本港從事醫務化驗工作的註冊要求。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">本人倡議特區政府可再度根據《輔助醫療業條例》( 第 359 章 ) 第 29(1A)條，將豁免註冊安排擴展到來自中國的物理治療師、職業治癒師、放射技師，視光師，以專職醫療舒緩人手不足。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc89f6982f734d9a7f0f1f130974c759de188b0","tid":2144171,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44cff1cf195e823e97d3a49651f429dec1596fb6","tid":2144171,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49074d807faeeb9bc72a761193b6e00c9e8d3428","tid":2144171,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc4043cfb075fe4c3515c616ca496e8e58091fc","tid":2144171,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"h